author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at an upcoming event known as "The Hatch", normally this would be just another day in an online game but somehow Roblox let a very shady character to take part in the event and when rightfully called out, they responded in the worst way possible. How? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!

title: Roblox Refuses To Stop Predators... (The Hatch)
